stm in a htmlwidget

December 01, 2015

library(stm)
library(stmBrowser)
library(pipeR)

# piped version of example in ?stm
textProcessor(
  documents=gadarian$open.ended.response
  ,metadata=gadarian
) %>>%
  (
    prepDocuments( .$documents, .$vocab, .$meta )
  ) %>>%
( ~out ) %>>% #save as out for later
  ({
    set.seed(02138)
    stm( .$documents, .$vocab, 20,
       prevalence=~treatment + s(pid_rep),
       data = .$meta 
    )
  }) %>>%
~ mod_out
